-- IMF To Reduce U.K. Growth Forecast Next Week: Telegraph
-- B y   L u c y   M e a k i n
-- 2012-10-06T09:59:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-06/imf-to-reduce-u-k-growth-forecast-next-week-telegraph.html
The International Monetary Fund is
also to downgrade outlook for global economy, London-based Daily
Telegraph says.
*IMF to say U.K. economy will contract 0.1 percent, from 0.2
percent expansion forecast in July: Telegraph
*Unidentified German newspaper reported global growth will be
revised down from 3.4 percent to 3.3 percent in 2012, and from
3.9 percent to 3.6 percent in 2013: Telegraph
*IMF sees euro zone shrinking 0.4 percent this year and growing
0.2 percent in 2013: Telegraph  To contact the reporter on this story:
